# ============================================================================
# OpenClaw on GCP — Devcontainer Environment Variables
#
# This file is a TEMPLATE. Copy it to `.devcontainer/.env` and fill in
# your actual values. The `.env` file is gitignored and never committed.
#
# These variables are injected into the devcontainer via runArgs --env-file.
#
# gcloud config (project, region) is stored in .devcontainer/.gcloud/
# which is bind-mounted into the container. Run `make auth` after rebuild.
# ============================================================================
